## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not account for the most recent developments in the oil market. Additionally, the complexity of global oil markets means that multiple factors can influence prices simultaneously, making it challenging to isolate specific causes. The reliance on secondary sources may also introduce biases inherent in the original reporting.